{"id":14747,"date":"2025-04-26T07:58:00","date_gmt":"2025-04-26T07:58:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/?p=14747"},"modified":"2026-01-13T08:44:11","modified_gmt":"2026-01-13T08:44:11","slug":"sam-precious-metals-hosts-colombian-ambassador","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/sam-precious-metals-hosts-colombian-ambassador\/","title":{"rendered":"Sam Precious Metals Hosts Colombian Ambassador to Advance UAE\u2013Colombia Economic Partnership"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"14747\" class=\"elementor elementor-14747\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b85306f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"98437\" data-id=\"b85306f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8ef5573\" data-eae-slider=\"73570\" data-id=\"8ef5573\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef96bb0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ef96bb0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>On Friday 11th July, 2025, Sam Precious Metals was honored to welcome H.E. Luis Miguel Merlano Hoyos, Ambassador of the Republic of Colombia to the UAE, for an official visit to our refinery in Dubai \u2013 marking a key moment in the evolving trade relationship between our two nations.<\/p><p>On April 19th, 2024, Colombia signed a Comprehensive Economic Partnership Agreement (CEPA) with the UAE, its most important trading partner in the Middle East. A year later, both countries continue to build on shared ambitions to enhance trade, improve market access, and foster cooperation in sectors ranging from renewable energy, elimination of customs tariffs on a wide range of goods, and infrastructure to sustainable mining.<\/p><p>As one of the most reputable refineries, globally, Sam was selected for this visit in recognition of our technical capabilities, robust management systems, and deep understanding of how local brands can succeed on the global stage.<\/p><p>These strengths uniquely position us to support the long-term goals of the CEPA framework \u2013 not only in precious metals trade, but also in cross-regional knowledge exchange and engineering collaboration.<br \/>With internationally recognized Fairmined and Fairtrade certifications, Sam is also deeply aligned with Colombia\u2019s commitment to environmental protection and ethical sourcing.<\/p><p>Our refinery\u2019s ongoing work with traceable, responsible supply chains reflects a shared belief that trade and sustainability must move forward together.<br \/>At a time when global trade dynamics are shifting, the UAE-Colombia partnership signals a bold step toward diversified economic growth and opening access to the broader South American market, and specifically Latin America. Sam Precious Metals is proud to contribute its expertise, network, and vision to this next chapter of international collaboration.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-55a25eb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"79404\" data-id=\"55a25eb\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a75e648\" data-eae-slider=\"31888\" data-id=\"a75e648\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a271d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4a271d7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}<\/style><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Sam Precious Metals accueille l\u2019Ambassadeur de Colombie pour renforcer le partenariat \u00e9conomique EAU\u2013Colombie<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7a7561 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e7a7561\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Le vendredi 11 juillet 2025, Sam Precious Metals a eu l\u2019honneur d\u2019accueillir S.E. Luis Miguel Merlano Hoyos, Ambassadeur de la R\u00e9publique de Colombie aux \u00c9mirats arabes unis, pour une visite officielle de notre raffinerie \u00e0 Duba\u00ef \u2013 marquant une \u00e9tape importante dans l\u2019\u00e9volution des relations commerciales entre nos deux pays.<\/p><p>Le 19 avril 2024, la Colombie a sign\u00e9e un Accord de Partenariat \u00c9conomique Global (CEPA) avec les \u00c9mirats arabes unis, son principal partenaire commercial au Moyen-Orient. Un an plus tard, les deux nations poursuivent leurs efforts pour renforcer le commerce, am\u00e9liorer l&#8217;acc\u00e8s au march\u00e9 et encourager la coop\u00e9ration dans des secteurs tels que les \u00e9nergies renouvelables, la suppression des droits de douane sur une large gamme de produits, les infrastructures et l\u2019exploitation mini\u00e8re durable.<\/p><p>En tant que l\u2019une des raffineries les plus r\u00e9put\u00e9es au monde, Sam a \u00e9t\u00e9 choisie pour cette visite en reconnaissance de ses capacit\u00e9s techniques, de ses syst\u00e8mes de gestion solides et de sa compr\u00e9hension approfondie de la r\u00e9ussite des marques locales sur la sc\u00e8ne mondiale. Ces atouts nous permettent de soutenir les objectifs \u00e0 long terme du CEPA \u2013 non seulement dans le commerce des m\u00e9taux pr\u00e9cieux, mais aussi dans le partage des connaissances interr\u00e9gional et la collaboration en ing\u00e9nierie.<\/p><p>Certifi\u00e9e Fairmined et Fairtrade \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9chelle internationale, Sam partage \u00e9galement l\u2019engagement de la Colombie en faveur de la protection de l\u2019environnement et de l\u2019approvisionnement \u00e9thique. Notre travail continu avec des cha\u00eenes d\u2019approvisionnement tra\u00e7ables et responsables refl\u00e8te une conviction commune : le commerce et la durabilit\u00e9 doivent progresser ensemble.<\/p><p>\u00c0 une \u00e9poque o\u00f9 les dynamiques commerciales mondiales \u00e9voluent, le partenariat EAU\u2013Colombie repr\u00e9sente une avanc\u00e9e audacieuse vers une croissance \u00e9conomique diversifi\u00e9e et un acc\u00e8s \u00e9largi au march\u00e9 sud-am\u00e9ricain, et plus particuli\u00e8rement \u00e0 l\u2019Am\u00e9rique latine. Sam Precious Metals est fi\u00e8re de mettre son expertise, son r\u00e9seau et sa vision au service de ce nouveau chapitre de coop\u00e9ration internationale.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-da54e85 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"57213\" data-id=\"da54e85\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1c2dada\" data-eae-slider=\"96435\" data-id=\"1c2dada\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55a1452 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"55a1452\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">\u0634\u0631\u0643\u0629 \u0633\u0627\u0645 \u0644\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062f\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0645\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u062a\u0633\u062a\u0642\u0628\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0642\u064a\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0648\u0644\u0648\u0645\u0628\u064a \u0644\u062a\u0639\u0632\u064a\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0631\u0627\u0643\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0642\u062a\u0635\u0627\u062f\u064a\u0629 \u0628\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0645\u0627\u0631\u0627\u062a \u0648 \u0643\u0648\u0644\u0648\u0645\u0628\u064a\u0627<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03b3a69 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"03b3a69\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u064a\u0648\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0648\u0627\u0641\u0642 11 \u064a\u0648\u0644\u064a\u0648 2025\u060c \u0643\u0627\u0646 \u0645\u0646 \u062f\u0648\u0627\u0639\u064a \u0634\u0631\u0641 \u0634\u0631\u0643\u0629 SAM \u0644\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062f\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0645\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u0627\u0633\u062a\u0642\u0628\u0627\u0644 \u0633\u0639\u0627\u062f\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0641\u064a\u0631 \u0644\u0648\u064a\u0633 \u0645\u064a\u063a\u064a\u0644 \u0645\u064a\u0631\u0644\u0627\u0646\u0648 \u0623\u0648\u062c\u0648\u0633\u060c \u0633\u0641\u064a\u0631 \u062c\u0645\u0647\u0648\u0631\u064a\u0629 \u0643\u0648\u0644\u0648\u0645\u0628\u064a\u0627 \u0644\u062f\u0649 \u062f\u0648\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0645\u0627\u0631\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062a\u062d\u062f\u0629\u060c \u0641\u064a \u0632\u064a\u0627\u0631\u0629 \u0631\u0633\u0645\u064a\u0629 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0645\u0635\u0641\u0627\u062a\u0646\u0627 \u0641\u064a \u062f\u0628\u064a \u2013 \u0645\u0645\u0627 \u0634\u0643\u0651\u0644 \u0644\u062d\u0638\u0629 \u0645\u0647\u0645\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u062a\u0637\u0648\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0642\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u062a\u062c\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0629 \u0628\u064a\u0646 \u0628\u0644\u062f\u064a\u0646\u0627<\/p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0641\u064a 19 \u0623\u0628\u0631\u064a\u0644 2024\u060c \u0648\u0642\u0651\u0639\u062a \u0643\u0648\u0644\u0648\u0645\u0628\u064a\u0627 \u0627\u062a\u0641\u0627\u0642\u064a\u0629 \u0634\u0631\u0627\u0643\u0629 \u0627\u0642\u062a\u0635\u0627\u062f\u064a\u0629 \u0634\u0627\u0645\u0644\u0629 \u0645\u0639 \u062f\u0648\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0645\u0627\u0631\u0627\u062a\u060c \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064a \u062a\u064f\u0639\u062f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0631\u064a\u0643 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u062c\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0647\u0645 \u0644\u0643\u0648\u0644\u0648\u0645\u0628\u064a\u0627 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u0646\u0637\u0642\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0631\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0648\u0633\u0637. \u0648\u0628\u0639\u062f \u0639\u0627\u0645 \u0645\u0646 \u062a\u0648\u0642\u064a\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u062a\u0641\u0627\u0642\u060c \u064a\u0648\u0627\u0635\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0644\u062f\u0627\u0646 \u062c\u0647\u0648\u062f\u0647\u0645\u0627 \u0644\u062a\u0639\u0632\u064a\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u062c\u0627\u0631\u0629\u060c \u0648\u062a\u062d\u0633\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0635\u0648\u0644 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0633\u0648\u0627\u0642\u060c \u0648\u062a\u0639\u0645\u064a\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u0627\u0648\u0646 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u062c\u0627\u0644\u0627\u062a \u0645\u062a\u0639\u062f\u062f\u0629 \u0645\u062b\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0627\u0642\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062a\u062c\u062f\u062f\u0629\u060c \u0648\u0625\u0644\u063a\u0627\u0621 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0633\u0648\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0631\u0643\u064a\u0629 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0645\u062c\u0645\u0648\u0639\u0629 \u0648\u0627\u0633\u0639\u0629 \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0644\u0639\u060c \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0628\u0646\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u062d\u062a\u064a\u0629\u060c \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u062f\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u062a\u062f\u0627\u0645<\/p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0648\u0628\u0627\u0639\u062a\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0647\u0627 \u0625\u062d\u062f\u0649 \u0623\u0643\u062b\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0635\u0627\u0641\u064a \u0634\u0647\u0631\u0629 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0645\u0633\u062a\u0648\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0645\u060c \u062a\u0645 \u0627\u062e\u062a\u064a\u0627\u0631 \u0634\u0631\u0643\u0629 SAM \u0644\u0647\u0630\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u064a\u0627\u0631\u0629 \u062a\u0642\u062f\u064a\u0631\u0627\u064b \u0644\u0642\u062f\u0631\u0627\u062a\u0647\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0642\u0646\u064a\u0629\u060c \u0648\u0623\u0646\u0638\u0645\u062a\u0647\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062f\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0648\u064a\u0629\u060c \u0648\u0641\u0647\u0645\u0647\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0645\u064a\u0642 \u0644\u0643\u064a\u0641\u064a\u0629 \u0646\u062c\u0627\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u062a\u062c\u0627\u0631\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u0644\u064a\u0629 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0627\u062d\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0645\u064a\u0629. \u0647\u0630\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0632\u0627\u064a\u0627 \u062a\u0624\u0647\u0644\u0646\u0627 \u0644\u062f\u0639\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0647\u062f\u0627\u0641 \u0637\u0648\u064a\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062f\u0649 \u0644\u0627\u062a\u0641\u0627\u0642\u064a\u0629 CEPA \u2013 \u0644\u064a\u0633 \u0641\u0642\u0637 \u0641\u064a \u062a\u062c\u0627\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062f\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0645\u064a\u0646\u0629\u060c \u0628\u0644 \u0623\u064a\u0636\u0627\u064b \u0641\u064a \u062a\u0628\u0627\u062f\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0631\u0641\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0642\u0644\u064a\u0645\u064a \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u0627\u0648\u0646 \u062